name: Nothing Has Happened In My Absence
description:
Sometimes we imagine what happens when we disappear, leave, or even die. What others will think of us, anyone who will feel our loss and miss us. In fact, we are only a small part of this life that if we were lost or gone, nothing would change and everything would go on as usual.
